{"tid":1255090,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人已經已經開始出現情緒病？","createTime":"2019-06-24T11:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T09:52:53.000Z","uid":261961,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"839ac2e452b255ab856ed8f85b799bacd6e51f56","tid":1255090,"uid":261961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510c0b045cd7805a22c6c497e71fa6fd57206b2e","tid":1255090,"uid":261961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33791ba0a4aec0815b3be204f2dcb731a0a2f598","tid":1255090,"uid":261961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"Topic都打錯左"},{"pid":"ee17ca5f5c06466852cb50c14803cde420ba17ba","tid":1255090,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:23:03.000Z","msg":"亂世中要有智慧同勇氣<br />\n藍屍親戚攻擊你圍攻你<br />\n點樣維持EQ都係一門學問<br />\n如果你夠足夠理據<br />\n唔洗怕佢地屌你係廢青<br />\n理性地同佢地理論<br />\n<br />\n如果真係崩潰邊緣<br />\n比自己抖下離開social media一陣<br />\n呢場戰唔係一時三刻<br />\n寧願休息一陣再抗爭<br />\n唔好一厥不振<br />\n加油全香港仲有好多人一齊奮鬥緊<br />\n你不孤單！"},{"pid":"6bd6ff7a8a4577119add65328de91f5ff4782a9e","tid":1255090,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1474f6c1a75ae7f9d32ee4aac62eaded66b2c0e","tid":1255090,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T12:33:12.000Z","msg":"攰就休息, 振作, 626再起動"},{"pid":"631a20860c74b04fcdf31c4893729e1d0c2bfaa9","tid":1255090,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"510c0b045cd7805a22c6c497e71fa6fd57206b2e","tid":1255090,"uid":261961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:16:28.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=0e630697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"60bdb0331b1e60aa27047aa7714e9acca71ed6b1","tid":1255090,"uid":84581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"只要你覺得係doing a right things<br />\n唔駛同意見不合既人交待<br />\n道不同不相為謀<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔會因為你耐心講解而轉軑"},{"pid":"23bdcef3da3f2d1f44999c15f0523637e93dce45","tid":1255090,"uid":265305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}